# Architecture

- **Deploy root**: `public/` served via Cloudflare Workers Static Assets (`wrangler.toml`).
- **Worker**: `src/index.js` — security headers + CSP on every response.
- **Content**: `public/assets/data/portfolio.json` fetched by `data.js`; exposes `window.portfolioDataReady`.
- **Boot**: `data.js` → `loader.js` → `boot.js` → `app.js` + Alpine → reveal/blur scripts → idle motion/liquid-hero.
- **No npm at runtime**; Tailwind built via `build-css.sh` + standalone CLI in `bin/` (gitignored).
- **JS modules**: `data.js`, `icons.js`, `loader.js`, `boot.js`, `app.js`, `reveal.js`, `blur-reveal.js`, `motion.js`, `liquid-hero.js`, `aurora.js`; vendors in `public/assets/js/vendor/`.
- **SW**: `public/sw.js` — network-first for `/assets/js/*` (except `/vendor/` → cache-first) and `/assets/css/*`; cache-first for other `/assets/*`.
- **Head sync**: `scripts/sync-head.js` generates marked blocks in `index.html`; do not edit inside sync markers.
- **Legacy**: an old `legacy/` dc-runtime site predated this rebuild and is **not** in the repo (gitignored) — nothing to extend.
- **No `eval` / `new Function`** in production code.
